text: Johannes Richter (born December 6, 1993) is a German professional basketball player for Gießen 46ers of the Basketball Bundesliga. ==Professional career== On 6 June 2016, Richter signed a two-year deal with Telekom Baskets Bonn. Richter signed with BBL newcomers Oettinger Rockets for the 2017–18 season. On August 14, 2020, he has signed with Gießen 46ers of the Basketball Bundesliga. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Baunach Young Pikes players Category:Brose Bamberg players Category:German men's basketball players Category:Power forwards (basketball) Category:Rockets (basketball club) players Category:s.Oliver Würzburg players Category:Skyliners Frankfurt players Category:Telekom Baskets Bonn players
